commit.message:
aarch64.c (generic_addrcost_table): Delete qi cost; add di cost.

2014-08-26  Evandro Menezes <e.menezes@samsung.com>

	* config/arm/aarch64/aarch64.c (generic_addrcost_table): Delete
	qi cost; add di cost.
	(cortexa57_addrcost_table): Likewise.

From-SVN: r214503

files.patch:
@@ -1,3 +1,9 @@
+2014-08-26  Evandro Menezes <e.menezes@samsung.com>
+
+	* config/arm/aarch64/aarch64.c (generic_addrcost_table): Delete
+	qi cost; add di cost.
+	(cortexa57_addrcost_table): Likewise.
+
 2014-08-26  Marek Polacek  <polacek@redhat.com>
 
 	PR c/61271

@@ -177,9 +177,9 @@ static const struct cpu_addrcost_table generic_addrcost_table =
   .addr_scale_costs =
 #endif
     {
-      NAMED_PARAM (qi, 0),
       NAMED_PARAM (hi, 0),
       NAMED_PARAM (si, 0),
+      NAMED_PARAM (di, 0),
       NAMED_PARAM (ti, 0),
     },
   NAMED_PARAM (pre_modify, 0),
@@ -198,9 +198,9 @@ static const struct cpu_addrcost_table cortexa57_addrcost_table =
   .addr_scale_costs =
 #endif
     {
-      NAMED_PARAM (qi, 0),
       NAMED_PARAM (hi, 1),

+      NAMED_PARAM (di, 0),
       NAMED_PARAM (ti, 1),
     },
   NAMED_PARAM (pre_modify, 0),
